##
#C  IsExternalSet . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . category of external sets
##
##  An external set  specifies an operation <opr>:  <D>  x <G>  --> <D>  of a
##  group <G> on a finite domain <D>. If <D> is not a list, an enumerator for
##  <D> is automatically chosen and fixed.
##
